Modern & Sweet good product Modern & Sweet There are many featuresLooking to celebrate Valentine’s Day with personalized photo cards? Fall in love with our new Valentine’s Day "Hugs & Kisses" card. Modern faux foil holiday design with one photo on the front and room for another and a custom message on the back. Holidays are an important part of any culture, and when the season arrives, it’s all about making new memories and having fun with family and friends. Family and friends will appreciate receiving Valentine’s Day Photo Cards customized with your favorite family photos and a personalized greeting. Add your custom wording to this design by using the "Edit this design template" boxes on the right hand side of the item, or click the blue "Customize it" button to arrange the text, change the fonts and colors and to also add additional information or images to this design. If you need any coordinating items, (thank you cards, etc.) please contact me for a custom order. ****For custom order, do not place this merchandize in your cart. Instead, click on the "contact seller" button and email me your request. A link to your merchandize will be emailed to you once the item is available. You can use that link to place your order.
